      • paste

        public boolean paste​(AbstractModel targetModel,
                     DrawnView targetView)
              throws PasteAbortedException
        Copies all objects from the system copy model to this view's model.
        Parameters:
        targetModel - the AbstractModel that will have the new components pasted in it.
        targetView - the DrawnView for adding drawn components.
        Throws:
        PasteAbortedException - if the paste operation is cancelled by the user.
